comment: Another great effort in the St George Single Malt line. Favorite so far
Delicious. But kinda tastes like weed. But still good.

wow! who would've thought St George could put out such an interesting whiskey. I had tried their Baller whiskey, and I can totally see how that one is influenced by this whiskey. complex and unique, certainly following traditional irish notes, this easily competes with big names at the $100 range
